trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for all strongly typed collections that manage <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en basisklasse for alle forespørselsparameter av sterk type samlinger som administrerer <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The StateManagedCollection class is the base class for all strongly typed collections that store <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> elements, including <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeBindingCollection>, and others.
trans-unit.target: Klassen StateManagedCollection er basisklasse for alle forespørselsparameter av sterk type samlinger som lagrer <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>elementer, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeBindingCollection>, og andre.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeBindingCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>

trans-unit.source: The StateManagedCollection collection manages its own state as well as the state of the elements it contains.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen StateManagedCollection administrerer sin egen stat i tillegg til status for elementene den inneholder.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, a call to <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A> saves the state of the collection and the state of all the elements currently contained by the collection.
trans-unit.target: Derfor et kall til <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A>lagrer tilstanden til samlingen og tilstanden for alle elementer som for øyeblikket finnes i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A>

trans-unit.source: The most important methods to consider when deriving from the StateManagedCollection class are <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Metodene som er viktigst skal vurdere når det avledes fra klassen StateManagedCollection er <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A> methods are used to store an index in view state for the type of a contained element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A>metoder brukes til å lagre en indeks i visningen tilstand for elementtypen en oppbevart.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.CreateKnownType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Storing an index rather than a fully qualified type name improves performance.
trans-unit.target: Lagring av en indeks i stedet for et fullstendig kvalifisert typenavn øker ytelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A> method is called whenever elements of the collection are manipulated, and validates the elements according to business rules.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>metoden kalles når elementer i samlingen er endres, og validerer elementer i henhold til forretningsregler.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Currently, the implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A> method prohibits `null` objects from being stored in the collection; however, you can override this method to define your own validation behavior in a derived type.
trans-unit.target: For øyeblikket implementeringen av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>metoden hindrer `null` objekter lagres i samlingen; du kan imidlertid overstyre denne metoden for å definere din egen validering-virkemåte i en avledet type.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnValidate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A> method forces the entire collection to be serialized to view state, rather than just serializing changes made to state since the last time it was loaded.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A>metoden tvinger hele samlingen serialiseres for å vise statusen, i stedet for serialisering bare endringer i tilstanden siden forrige gang det ble lastet inn.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A> method is an abstract method you can implement to perform this same behavior at the element level.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A>metoden er en abstrakt du kan implementere for å utføre denne samme virkemåten på elementnivå.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.SetDirtyObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > StateManagedCollection stores assembly-qualified type names of the collection items in view state.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > StateManagedCollection lagrer samlingen kvalifisert typenavn samling elementene i visningen tilstand.

trans-unit.source: A site visitor could decode the view state and retrieve the type name.
trans-unit.target: Noen kan dekode visningsstatusen og hente Typenavnet.

trans-unit.source: If this scenario creates a security concern in your Web site, you can manually encrypt the type name before placing it in the view state.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dette scenarioet oppretter et sikkerhetsproblem på webområdet, kan du manuelt kryptere typenavnet før du setter i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Derived classes can override the constructor to provide customized implementation.
trans-unit.target: Avledede klasser kan overstyre konstruktøren for å angi tilpassede implementering.

trans-unit.source: Removes all items from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle elementer fra de <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClear%2A> method is called before the Clear method is called, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClearComplete%2A> method is called after Clear has finished removing elements from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClear%2A>-metoden før metoden Fjern kalles, og <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClearComplete%2A>-metoden etter at Fjern er fullført fjerner elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClearComplete%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.OnClear%2A>

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection to an array, starting at a particular array index.
trans-unit.target: Overfører av elementene i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samling til en matrise, med Start fra en bestemt matriseindeksen.

trans-unit.source: The specified array must be of a compatible type.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte matrisen må være kompatibelt.

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Elementene kopieres til den <xref:System.Array>i samme rekkefølge som enumeratoren går gjennom den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> </xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>som er målet for elementene kopieres fra den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` som kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: array is .
trans-unit.target: arrayis .

trans-unit.source: index is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: indexer mindre enn null.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements contained in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: The number of elements contained in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Antallet elementer i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, creates an instance of a class that implements <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, oppretter du en forekomst av en klasse som implementerer <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The type of object created is based on the specified member of the collection returned by the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*> method.
trans-unit.target: Objekttypen opprettes basert på det angitte medlemmet i samlingen ble returnert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*>

trans-unit.source: The CreateKnownType method is called internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> collection in its implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23LoadViewState%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateKnownType kalles internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>samlingen i implementeringen av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23LoadViewState%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23LoadViewState%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: Derived collections override the CreateKnownType method to return a default instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> type identified by the provided `index`, which maps to one of the types returned by the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Avledede samlinger overstyre metoden CreateKnownType for å returnere en default-forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>typen som ble identifisert av den angitte `index`, som kobles til en av typene som er returnert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>

trans-unit.source: The index, from the ordered list of types returned by <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*>, of the type of <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> to create.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen, fra i listen over typer som returneres av <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*>, av typen for <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> til å opprette.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetKnownTypes*>

trans-unit.source: An instance of a class derived from , according to the index provided.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av en klasse som er avledet fra , i henhold til den index angitt.

trans-unit.source: In all cases when not overridden in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: I alle tilfeller der ikke overstyres i en avledet klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an iterator that iterates through the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer løkkesyntaks går gjennom den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> that can be used to iterate through the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> types that the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection can contain.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, får du en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> datatyper som i <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samling kan inneholde.

trans-unit.source: The GetKnownTypes method is called internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> collection in its implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetKnownTypes kalles internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>samlingen i implementeringen av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Web%23UI%23IStateManager%23SaveViewState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: Derived collections override the GetKnownTypes method to return an array of <xref:System.Type> objects that represent the types the collection can contain.
trans-unit.target: Avledede samlinger overstyre metoden GetKnownTypes for å returnere en matrise av <xref:System.Type>objekter som representerer typene i samlingen kan inneholde.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: An ordered array of <xref:System.Type> objects that identify the types of <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> objects the collection can contain.
trans-unit.target: Tabelldata i med <xref:System.Type>objekter som identifiserer hvilke typer <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> objekter samlingen kan inneholde.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The default implementation returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, performs additional work before the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*> method removes all items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, utfører ekstra arbeidet før den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*>metoden fjerner alle elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*>

trans-unit.source: Collections derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> can override the OnClear method to perform any additional work before all items are removed from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Samlinger som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>kan overstyre metoden OnClear for å utføre flere arbeid før alle elementene skal fjernes fra samlingen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, performs additional work after the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*> method finishes removing all items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, utfører ekstra arbeid etter den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*>metoden er ferdig med å fjerne alle elementene fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear*>

trans-unit.source: Collections derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> can override the OnClearComplete method to perform any additional work after all items are removed from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Samlinger som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>kan overstyre metoden OnClearComplete for å utføre flere arbeid etter at alle elementer er fjernet fra samling ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, performs additional work before the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Insert%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Add%2A> method adds an item to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, utfører ekstra arbeidet før den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Insert%2A> eller <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Add%2A> metoden legger til et element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Collections derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> can override the OnInsert method to perform any additional work before an item is added to the collection using the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Add%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.System%23Collections%23IList%23Insert%2A> method.

trans-unit.source: View state is the accumulation of the values of a server control's properties.
trans-unit.target: Visningsstatusen er summen av verdiene i en serverkontroll egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: These values are automatically placed in the server control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A> property, which is an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag> class.
trans-unit.target: Disse verdiene plasseres automatisk i server kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>egenskapen som er en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property's value is then persisted to a string object after the save state stage of the server control life cycle.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen er deretter beholdt i en strengobjektet når lagringen tilstand fase av server kontrollen levetid.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the collection and collection elements' state to restore.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som representerer samlingen og Samlingselementer, tilstanden til å gjenopprette.

trans-unit.source: Saves the changes to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection and each <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> object it contains since the time the page was posted back to the server.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer endringer i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samlingen og hver <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> objektet den. siden siden ble posteres tilbake til serveren.

trans-unit.source: This method is used primarily by control developers.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere.

trans-unit.source: View state is the accumulation of the values of a server control's properties.
trans-unit.target: Visningsstatusen er summen av verdiene i en serverkontroll egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: These values are automatically placed in the server control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A> property, which is an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag> class.
trans-unit.target: Disse verdiene plasseres automatisk i server kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>egenskapen som er en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property's value is then persisted to a string object after the save state stage of the server control life cycle.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen er deretter beholdt i en strengobjektet når lagringen tilstand fase av server kontrollen levetid.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [NIB: ASP.NET Web Server Controls](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e18eb2f2-cf00-47ae-b1a1-dfc188a6dea1).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [NIB: Kontroller i ASP.NET Web Server](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e18eb2f2-cf00-47ae-b1a1-dfc188a6dea1).

trans-unit.source: When view state is saved, this string object is returned to the client as a variable that is stored in an HTML hidden element (`<input type="hidden">`).
trans-unit.target: Når visningsstatusen lagres, strengobjektet returneres til klienten som en variabel som er lagret i et skjult HTML-element (`<input type="hidden">`).

trans-unit.source: When you author custom server controls, you can improve efficiency by overriding this method and modifying your server control's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Når du skriver egendefinerte serverkontroller, du kan forbedre effektiviteten av overstyrer denne metoden, og endre din serverkontroll <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewState%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [NIB: ASP.NET Web Server Controls](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e18eb2f2-cf00-47ae-b1a1-dfc188a6dea1) and[ASP.NET State Management Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [NIB: Kontroller i ASP.NET Web Server](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e18eb2f2-cf00-47ae-b1a1-dfc188a6dea1) og[ASP.NET oversikt over tilstand](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The object that contains the changes to the view state of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> and the items it contains.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som inneholder endringer i visningsstatusen for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> og elementer den inneholder.

trans-unit.source: If no view state is associated with the collection and its elements, this method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen visningsstatus er knyttet til samlingen og elementene, metoden returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Causes the <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"></xref> collection and each of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"></xref> objects it contains to track changes to their view state so they can be persisted across requests for the same page.
trans-unit.target: Gjør den <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection"> </xref> samlingen og hver av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.IStateManager"> </xref> objekter den. Hvis du vil spore endringer i sine visningsstatus slik at de kan beholdes på tvers av forespørsler for samme side.
